---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import gina from '../images/gina.jpg'
---

<style>
  .gina-image {
    float: left;
    margin-right: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    height: 200px;
    width: auto;
  }
</style>
<BaseLayout pageBackground>
  <article class="body-width">
    <h1>About Belle Maison</h1>
    <Image src={gina} alt="Gina Schorr" class="gina-image" />
    <p>
      Everyone who comes to Belle Maison has a vision of how they want their lifestyle
      reflected in their home. At Belle Maison, we believe in making those visions a
      reality. By combining form, function, color, and texture, we collaborate with you to
      create a beautiful and comfortable living space that truly feels like home.
    </p>
    <p>
      With over 20 years of interior design experience, Belle Maison has the expertise and
      passion to transform your home into a welcoming and timeless environment. We bring a
      keen awareness of what it takes to create lasting designs, utilizing texture, color,
      lighting, textiles, and interior finishes. Your home should reflect who you are—not
      your designer. We consider both form and function to craft a space that represents
      you and enhances every aspect of your life. Your home is your castle, and it should
      always surround you with beauty, comfort, and calm.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Process</h2>
    <p>
      At Belle Maison, we know that no two clients are alike. Your needs and tastes are
      unique, so we don’t believe in a one-size-fits-all solution. Our process begins with
      a face-to-face meeting where we get to know you and your vision. We’ll ask
      questions, brainstorm ideas, explore all possibilities, and discuss a budget that
      works for you.
    </p>
    <p>
      Together, we’ll define your starting point and develop a customized plan to
      transform your home into the functional and beautiful space you’ve envisioned. From
      initial concepts to the final touches, we’ll guide you through every step, ensuring
      that your design goals become a reality.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
